Fixed: When watching live content Philo would sometimes allow you to seek into the future. Our app would helpfully close itself to prepare for time travel. Now it doesn t. Fixed: In some situations we d show that you had watched 100 of an episode whether you actually did or not. There are some cases where it s cool to get credit for something you didn t do. This is not one of them. Fixed: When switching back to the Philo app it could take up to a full minute for tiles to refresh. Now it takes less time. Much less. Like it happens instantaneously.
